Escha? What's the matter? Why are you staring at
the window? Is there anything particular... Ah, apple trees!

Escha, Escha.
Would you like some apples?

Ah, no.
I just remember things of my family.

Escha's family?
Is it related to apples?
Yes. My family are apple farmers.

The harvests were very poor in recent years.
But our apples are very delicious...

When I saw that tree, I began to think about our harvest
this year. I really want to go back and help picking apples...

... Apples in your world
must be very delicious.

Yes! They are stuffed with honey,
and are super sweet!

It is very good no matter you eat it directly, or use if for
desserts or for dishes!

Ah, haw-haw, look how excited you are...
You really do love apples.
You can have as many apples as you want here!
Apples in Olbius are delicious too, huh?

Uh hee hee. Indeed, Olbius' apples
are quite yummy too!

Yes, very delicious!
And they look pretty...

But... Apples from Colseit
are even better than Olbius' apples!

Er, really that delicious?
I want to taste Colseit's apples already... (Swallowing)

Uh-huh! If I have a chance,
I really want you to try the apples from Colseit...

But, I must find the way to go back
to the world I came from...

Ha-ha, don't worry too much.
I am sure you'll find it!

If you find the way to go back to your world,
let's see which world's apples are more delicious!

Good idea!
I can't wait to try Colseit's apples!

When that time comes, I'll treat you with
the apples I am proud of!

Great! Let's cheer up and help Escha to find a way
to go back her world, [px]!
